commandDescription: display a list of IDs and general information about debug logs
longDescription:
Run this command in a project to list the IDs and general information for all debug logs in your default org.
To fetch a specific log from your org, obtain the ID from this command's output, then run the “sfdx force:apex:log:get” command.
logLevelDescription: logging level for this command invocation
logLevelLongDescription: The logging level for this command invocation. Logs are stored in $HOME/.sfdx/sfdx.log.
no_debug_logs_found: No debug logs found in org
